 Thursday Aug 30th Monasteri : reveill 6.30 am : parad for Coy : I seen the M.O. re our mess about late : wrote in morn : gas parad lectur on the new gas that is be use it is not too pleasant at all : post H.C. card two Bapaum P.C.s to Mother Friday Aug 31st Monasteri : reveill 6.30 am : boy on a " stunt " : we had to fall in for parad befor dinner also afternoon parad but sat down watch the other drill : they seem frighten to see us S.B.s off parad at all : wrote after tea Saturday Sept 1st Monasteri : reveill 6.30 am : Rout march with full pack in morn : paid 20 Franc in afternoon : showeri weather so wrote after tea : rotten weather altogeth late
